<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٤٣٨٩ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5788">‌مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ عُبَيْدٍ، </a>نَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1619">‌حَمَّادٌ، </a><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٢٣٨⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>نَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6932">‌يَحْيَى </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5978">‌مُحَمَّدِ بْنِ يَحْيَى بْنِ حَبَّانَ </a>بِهَذَا الْحَدِيثِ،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> فَجَلَدَهُ مَرْوَانُ جَلَدَاتٍ وَخَلَّى سَبِيلَهُ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>